org.emocha.model.entities
Class FormDataFile

java.lang.Object
  org.emocha.model.entities.FormDataFile

public class FormDataFile
extends java.lang.Object

FormDatafile represents any file associated to a form. Stored in the database but relationship is with the FormData entity. Files are usually sent to the server from the devices.
